highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Lucknow. “Kesariya” is the highest at #1.
“Jiske Aane Se Mukammal” by Prashant Katheriya is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Lucknow, up 46 spots at #23.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Lucknow the longest, at 56 weeks straight.
“Heer Ranjha” by Rito Riba, Rajat Nagpal, and Rana Sotal is the highest new entry on Top Songs Lucknow at #18.
